list.t:
As designed, PTP expects a multicast communication model;
            however, PTP also supports a unicast communication model as long
            as the behavior of the protocol is preserved.

section.t:
Online gaming is a significant part of the gaming market;
           however, latency can degrade the end user's experience. For example,
           "First Person Shooter" (FPS) games are highly delay sensitive.

For VR, a maximum delay of
1&nbhy;10 ms is needed;
            if doing remote VR, the total network delay budget is 1-5 ms.
